Remarks.
Previous records in São Paulo include Ilhabela (Ilha de São Sebastião) (
Mossolin & Mantelatto 2008
). The species is found in freshwater drainages close to the coast. The phylogeny and taxonomy of the genus is complex, and a recent study elucidated this scenario (
Souza-Carvalho & Mantelatto 2017
). Sequences accession number (GenBank): CCDB 2672—16S (
KF688003
), COI (
KF688055
) (
Souza-Carvalho & Mantelatto 2017
).
